<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Preferences Saved</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
           background: #f5f5f5; color: #222; padding: 32px 16px;
           display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 24px;
            max-width: 420px; width: 100%; text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    p { color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .week { font-weight: 600; color: #222; }
    a { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; color: #3a7af5; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">✅</div>
    <h1>Preferences saved</h1>
    <p>Week of <span class="week"><%= @week_start.strftime('%A, %B %-d') %></span></p>
    <p style="margin-top:12px;">Close this tab and tap <strong>↺ Regenerate</strong> in Telegram to apply your preferences.</p>
    <a href="/week">← Edit again</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
